PrecisEnactment of the MAXIMUM AMOUNT FOR AGREEMENTS WITH GOVERNMENTS ORDER - which authorizes the Interim Commissioner of Nunavut to enter into various kinds of Agreements with other governments where the maximum total amount that the Government of Nunavut must pay under its terms is $15,000,000.

precis:
Enactment of the MAXIMUM AMOUNT FOR AGREEMENTS WITH GOVERNMENTS ORDER -
which authorizes the Interim Commissioner of Nunavut to enter into various
kinds of Agreements with other governments where the maximum total amount
that the Government of Nunavut must pay under its terms is $15,000,000.
